i've always known i wanted children from about the age of 3. for some strange reason living thought everything that i have just having the idea that one day i'll be able to have a child of my own who i'll love and who'll love me unconditionaly is what kept me going. knowing that one day life will grow from inside and grow and blosom into a beautiful human being amazes me still. the idea that to people can create a life from nothing visible to the human eye is strange yet amazing!  a smiling face, curious eyes, round cheeks and nothing but love. a fresh new canvas ready to be painted with all the colours of the world.
 
no one should ever hit a child, hurt them to the point that they cry and beg and scream for it to stop. nothing should be a reason to beat a child, to leave them mentally scared for life....
thanks for visiting, this journal is friends only so comment to be added and all that xo.
